{
  "stem": "5496.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But we had these terrible zahlappells, which are infamous by now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "People seem to realize just what it was, twice a day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we felt so bad for our mother, standing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I have two things I remember about Auchwitz-- the blazing sun, and the mud.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was always gray, and muddy, and cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we had no clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And for hours on end, we were standing for the count.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But we were never beaten, and we were never sent to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it must have been very early, because it was still dark.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they herded us out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I guess that's when you had the facilities for the infamous toilets, which, luckily, I don't remember much of.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then there were-- all I remember, standing outside in rows of five, to the best of my recollection.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they counted, and counted, and recounted us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And whoever couldn't stand, of course, passed out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was no end to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we were herded back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, I guess, came the meal, which consisted of some kind of a black liquid with bread that the girls put certain-- girls were-- I don't know that they were volunteers, or they were drafted to bring it from the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were given that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we just stayed, until the next zahlappell, which wasn't too long after.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that went on, day in, day out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We slept in-- on these wooden bunks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were about five of us to each row.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we tried to keep neat and clean and wash ourselves as much as we could, of course.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was getting increasingly difficult.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We started to lose weight, rapidly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And things got from bad to worse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were looking over with envy.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
